292
00:13:09,084 --> 00:13:11,474
I understand now what Sahashi-san meant.

293
00:13:13,333 --> 00:13:15,130
That Mamiya-san is amazing!

294
00:13:16,498 --> 00:13:17,310
But

295
00:13:18,193 --> 00:13:19,724
