302
00:13:43,264 --> 00:13:44,966
Could you check the stock for me?

303
00:13:44,990 --> 00:13:46,381
Sure. Have a good trip.

304
00:13:46,521 --> 00:13:47,958
Thank you. I appreciate it.

305
00:13:47,981 --> 00:13:48,754
Yes.

306
00:13:50,435 --> 00:13:51,365
Has Mamiya-san

307
00:13:51,443 --> 00:13:53,178
