319
00:14:15,138 --> 00:14:16,631
Yes, of course.

320
00:14:16,779 --> 00:14:18,748
- Thank you very much.
- I'll do it my way.

321
00:14:19,060 --> 00:14:21,068
Please come again.

322
00:14:21,748 --> 00:14:23,013
Focus on the task at hand.

323
00:14:27,154 --> 00:14:28,334
And finally,

324
00:14:30,928 --> 00:14:33,709
