338
00:15:22,553 --> 00:15:23,670
Maybe I should delete it.

339
00:15:26,295 --> 00:15:27,084
No,

340
00:15:27,935 --> 00:15:29,185
it's fine.

341
00:15:30,287 --> 00:15:32,185
I need to tell Sahashi properly.

342
00:15:38,451 --> 00:15:40,793
