345
00:15:47,771 --> 00:15:49,060
Excuse me.

346
00:15:49,224 --> 00:15:50,373
Thank you very much.

347
00:15:50,802 --> 00:15:52,099
This one may...

348
00:15:52,162 --> 00:15:55,099
- The day was busy with many customers.
- Please come again.

349
00:15:56,201 --> 00:15:58,474
We barely had a moment to breathe,

350
00:15:59,771 --> 00:16:01,131
