359
00:16:23,256 --> 00:16:24,217
I'm sorry,

360
00:16:24,396 --> 00:16:25,982
I was at work until now.

361
00:16:26,342 --> 00:16:27,942
I was in the neighborhood.

362
00:16:27,967 --> 00:16:29,959
So, can you make it today?

363
00:16:31,474 --> 00:16:32,279
Ah...

364
00:16:40,662 --> 00:16:42,177
(I want to see you)

365
00:16:42,178 --> 00:16:44,865
(Sahashi: Me too)

366
00:16:45,645 --> 00:16:46,599
Are you okay?

367
00:16:50,693 --> 00:16:51,646
I'm sorry!

368
00:16:52,240 --> 00:16:53,287
I can't go!

369
00:16:53,826 --> 00:16:55,276
It's really urgent.

370
00:16:55,896 --> 00:16:56,803
I'm sorry!

371
00:16:57,623 --> 00:16:58,287
Huh?

372
00:16:58,771 --> 00:16:59,888
Natsume-kun!

373
00:17:12,146 --> 00:17:13,099
Toma!

374
00:17:20,107 --> 00:17:20,912
Toma!

375
00:17:22,045 --> 00:17:22,888
Sorry.

376
00:17:29,013 --> 00:17:30,318
I was too harsh too.

377
00:17:33,279 --> 00:17:34,638
But why are you here?

378
00:17:35,326 --> 00:17:36,724
What about the dinner with Emma?

379
00:17:37,623 --> 00:17:38,654
What?

380
00:17:40,615 --> 00:17:41,880
Is it so wrong to prioritize

381
00:17:41,905 --> 00:17:43,025
