382
00:17:46,709 --> 00:17:47,865
Natsume-san.

383
00:17:48,756 --> 00:17:50,060
Don't look at me like that.

384
00:17:51,287 --> 00:17:52,232
I feel like hugging you

385
00:17:52,240 --> 00:17:53,365
and never letting go.

386
00:17:56,748 --> 00:17:57,521
Come.

387
00:18:14,141 --> 00:18:15,055
I...

388
00:18:16,758 --> 00:18:18,414
I know you're putting

389
00:18:18,422 --> 00:18:19,500
in a lot of effort.

390
00:18:22,485 --> 00:18:24,313
But I'm envious of your talent

391
00:18:27,188 --> 00:18:28,508
and feel inferior…

392
00:18:33,688 --> 00:18:35,633
I'm used to being seen that way.

393
00:18:38,688 --> 00:18:40,133
During my model days,

394
00:18:40,954 --> 00:18:43,508
I was targeted by male senpai models.

395
00:18:46,743 --> 00:18:48,891
When I really tried, I was dragged down.

396
00:18:51,243 --> 00:18:51,993
You...

397
00:18:53,469 --> 00:18:54,610
That's why then...

398
00:18:56,133 --> 00:18:58,087
I don't get serious about anything.

399
00:19:01,321 --> 00:19:02,024
Yes.

400
00:19:03,001 --> 00:19:04,923
I thought it's useless to be serious.

401
00:19:08,563 --> 00:19:09,524
But I...

402
00:19:11,126 --> 00:19:13,680
I think Sahashi is really cool!

403
00:19:18,704 --> 00:19:19,844
So, I...

404
00:19:22,227 --> 00:19:25,532
