407
00:19:36,657 --> 00:19:38,016
and I feel pathetic…

408
00:19:47,055 --> 00:19:48,673
I'm sorry for saying such awful things.

409
00:19:52,907 --> 00:19:53,758
But I

410
00:19:55,352 --> 00:19:57,008
really, really like you.

411
00:20:07,337 --> 00:20:08,290
I'm sorry too.

412
00:20:15,110 --> 00:20:16,680
It's true I was annoyed by you

413
00:20:16,705 --> 00:20:18,385
acting out of character,

414
00:20:19,555 --> 00:20:20,423
but I was

415
00:20:22,915 --> 00:20:24,375
really frustrated with myself

416
00:20:24,384 --> 00:20:26,584
when you were sick at that time.

417
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:29,415
I'm truly sorry.

418
00:20:33,008 --> 00:20:35,149
But you don't understand at all.

419
00:20:39,492 --> 00:20:41,732
Even if you don't try to match me,

420
00:20:43,079 --> 00:20:44,977
I respect you.

421
00:20:47,141 --> 00:20:48,149
Besides,

422
00:20:52,985 --> 00:20:54,266
I really like you.

423
00:21:00,985 --> 00:21:03,196
You just called me by name earlier.

424
00:21:05,413 --> 00:21:06,171
Well,

425
00:21:07,508 --> 00:21:09,290
you told me to…

426
00:21:11,157 --> 00:21:12,454
When I was thinking about you,

427
00:21:13,235 --> 00:21:14,469
I just blurted it out.

428
00:21:16,618 --> 00:21:18,477
You were thinking about me all the time?

429
00:21:19,711 --> 00:21:20,711
I'm happy.

430
00:21:36,477 --> 00:21:37,618
Let's make up.

431
00:21:40,812 --> 00:21:41,665
Yeah.

432
00:21:44,094 --> 00:21:45,351
