443
00:22:10,930 --> 00:22:12,079
Of course.

444
00:22:23,974 --> 00:22:24,833
Here.

445
00:22:35,415 --> 00:22:36,110
Mhm.

446
00:23:04,282 --> 00:23:05,438
Sahashi.

447
00:23:07,891 --> 00:23:09,094
