450
00:23:24,462 --> 00:23:25,415
I like you.

451
00:23:30,344 --> 00:23:31,641
To say ‘I like you'…

452
00:23:32,337 --> 00:23:33,594
It's amazing.

453
00:23:35,235 --> 00:23:36,250
The heart that was

454
00:23:36,275 --> 00:23:37,955
